# Student Record Manager (CLI)

## ğŸ“Œ Project Description
Student Record Manager is a Command-Line Interface (CLI) based Python application designed to manage student records efficiently. 

The system allows users to:
- Add student details
- View all student records
- Search student by roll number
- Calculate average marks
- Display topper (highest marks)
- Exit the application

This project is developed to practice Python fundamentals such as:
- Classes and Objects
- Lists
- Conditional statements
- Loops
- Functions
- User input handling

